data.description: *VA assumable loan, even for non-VA at 5.125%* This is a dream home! In the plains of Skagit county with year-round sunset views of Mount Erie over Anacortes. You would never know you are minutes away from "town". With ALL major shopping destinations. Its country living at its best. Enjoy friends and family over for a BBQ on the nice, covered deck. Plenty of room for gardening, lots of storage and room for toys with its large shop and storage barn. Newly landscaped yard that changes glory with the seasons. New split rail fence with burning bushes for fall! Beautiful healthy old oak provides shade in the fully fenced back yard. Double primary suites are rare. BUT this has it! Virtual tour available.
